tags.name: Friday Street
tags.wheelchair:description: 2m barrier at entrance, gravel surface. No wheelchair friendly walks start from here. Information boards. Steep narrow lane to village.

tags.note: Only knew south and north edges.

tags.name: Starveall Corner Car Park
tags.wheelchair:description: Uneven surfaces. Only suitable for cross country powered chairs. 1200m to Leith Hill Tower via uneven and muddy paths.
Small car park, usually very muddy and rutted.
